com.khalsa_ji.ems.builder

Class EmployeeBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.khalsa_ji.ems.builder.EmployeeBuilder

  • public class EmployeeBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    The class EmployeeBuilder is a Builder class for the Employee class. It helps in instantiating instances of Employee class by providing a set of methods based on the Builder Design Pattern.
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ravikiran Singh
    See Also:
    Employee, Designation
